  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/48c1b80b376067a95edb7d2429f723a9.avif?t=1738065375\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Your favourite Cry Babies characters are ready to play! <br><br>The Big Game is a friendly and fun adventure perfect for young players. Join Lady, Coney, Dreamy and friends in an all-new adventure as they take part in an exciting multi-stage tournament to win the fabled Golden Pacifier! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/5674fff1ca0818a17119de0b839e1549.webp?t=1738065375\" width=616 height=51 /></span><br><br>Players can meet and play as 15 popular Cry Babies characters, and explore familiar locations from Baby Bottle Valley to Fantasy Mountain, Tutti Frutti Bay, Icy World and finally to a new planet, Planet Tear! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/cd55e4d9bb1ff2119636100cb0f97abf.avif?t=1738065375\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/550584ef88339446cd3a790309965110.webp?t=1738065375\" width=616 height=51 /></span><br><br>Take part in lots of fun activities to progress, including hide and seek, mazes, puzzles, dancing, taking photos and even having a bath!  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/123b216f4a8d9bf896005011e1f60670.avif?t=1738065375\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/8c8467200a5c982512f68639ae827885.webp?t=1738065375\" width=616 height=51 /></span><br><br>Cry Babies love their friends, so just use a second controller and two players can cooperate for double the fun! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/d738a385991e810deaf976e7b516ccdb.avif?t=1738065375\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/5c8f31965d46290b24f0bd05fb054354.webp?t=1738065375\" width=616 height=51 /></span><br><br>Collect pink stars by exploring then spend them on new clothes and outfits for your favourite characters! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/72680bf2545ee8c95df233ea6360c991.avif?t=1738065375\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/b64745599ab296e3686e72641aef673d.webp?t=1738065375\" width=616 height=51 /></span><br><br>All story scenes are animated and voiced just like the TV series, so players will feel they’re taking part in a whole new interactive episode! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/d6d891af34ae2f4b4f8a6626d0a7a4e9.avif?t=1738065375\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Each victory takes them to a new world from their popular animated series. From Baby Bottle Valley to Fantasy Mountain, Tutti Frutti Bay, Icy World and finally to a new planet, Planet Tear! Along the way they’ll play hide and seek, dance, dress up, explore mazes and solve puzzles. They can even stop to take a bath! <br><br>Despite the glittering prize, the Cry Babies always work together to help each other succeed!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/d5aa2b15a6f95f0515c77900ccf2c5ab.avif?t=1738065375\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
